# Monthly-traffic baseline: derived data is script-populated and re-fetchable
# (dataset 2708 is CC0, monthly, restated by immutable resource id), so a
# committed snapshot would go stale on the next backfill. Ignore the specific
# files only — the live-logger DBs (queues/echerha/dpsu) stay tracked, and the
# raw XLSX in data/raw_traffic/ is kept as a stable per-vintage provenance anchor.
data/monthly_traffic.db
data/monthly_traffic.csv
